        "Name": "The Paperfold University Student Handbook — Comments on the 43rd Revised Edition",
        "Desc": "A record of teachers' evaluations towards revisions to the student handbook. You get a real sense of the free and unrestrained school spirit of Paperfold University from the discussions within.",
        "World": 4,
