        "Name": "Memorial to the Illustrious Officials Xiao and Hong",
        "Desc": "In the battle against the Disciples of Sanctus Medicus, a pair of foxian brothers bravely sacrificed their lives. Their comrades wrote obituaries in traditional foxian manners to express their grief and to commemorate the two martyrs.",
