                "Desc": "Full sets of gear and equipment — guidance from elite coaches — a positive training atmosphere. Your healthy transformation begins now!<br><br>Don't worry about your social circles<br>Run circles around the gym, instead!<br><br>Those busier than you work out here<br>Those richer than you work out here<br>Those who live longer than you work out here<br><br>Who will be richer in 200 years?<br>Who will have higher status in 400 years?<br>Who'll be the healthier in 600 years?<br><br>Why build my body?<br>How strong is a delve's gravity?<br>Time will tell you —<br>Without skeletal support, your muscles and skin will keep sagging. Keep training to ward off the aging process!"
