                "Name": "Prescription: Draught of Draconic Surge",
                "Desc": "This prescription is for those with a foundation in martial arts, or for those in better physical condition than average.<br>Long's Scions should not use this prescription.<br><br>Formula: <br><i>Daiyu Angelica 7 mace</i><br><i>Frost Mulberry 3 mace</i><br><i>Lunarescent Sea Cucumber 1 mace</i><br><i>2 dried Thalassa dung beetles (pounded)</i><br><i>1 dried Fanghu seahorse (pounded)</i><br><i>Distill and extract. Filter until clear.</i><br><i>Let cool until room temperature and dilute with the Lunarescent Depths water by a 1:1 ratio.</i><br><i>Take out 1 gram of Vidyadhara bone marrow (live sample) and immerse it in the mixture for 12 dual-hours.</i><br><i>Use an acupuncture needle to administer a deep muscular injection of the medicine.</i><br><br>Taking this medicine normally may induce severe pain all over the body, abnormal bone noises, plus partial loss of sight and hearing.<br>Those who manage to survive this will attain the way of immortality.<br><br>Mercy of Sanctus Medicus, the Arbor's new growth."
